cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB port for S1U to 0, an invalid port number, will cause connection failures during the NG-U interface setup and prevent proper data transmission.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_ul to [0, 0] causes timing misalignment in the uplink compression, leading to synchronization failures and data transmission errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_ul 設定為 [0, 0] 會導致上行壓縮中的時序錯位，造成同步失敗和數據傳輸錯誤。
